[{'filename': 'registration_number_meta.json', 'options': {'sql': "SELECT    registration_number,
          businesses,
          location,
          classification,
          classifications,
          cardsales,
          CASE
              WHEN    places.places.merchant_name IS NOT NULL AND location IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT(
                                                                              location.sido, ' ',
                                                                              location.sigungu, ' ',
                                                                              location.dong, ' ',
                                                                              places.places.merchant_name
                                                                         )
              WHEN    places.places.merchant_name IS NOT NULL  THEN places.places.merchant_name
              ELSE    null
          END AS search_name,

          named_struct(
              'name', places.places.merchant_name,
              'reviews', places.reviews
          ) AS places
FROM      merge
WHERE     registration_number IS NOT NULL"}, 'role': 'process', 'type': 'sql'}]
